data.description: Welcome to this inviting home that boasts an open concept design. You'll find an oversized island beautifully adorned with granite countertops, a gas range, and a convenient pantry in the kitchen. But that's not all; this home also features several new additions in 2022. You'll enjoy newly installed LVP floors, a smart refrigerator, dishwasher, washer and dryer with pedestals, new light fixtures, toilets, freshly painted and a fenced-in yard. Additionally, the garage is equipped with mounted storage racks. The primary suite is a true retreat, providing excellent separation from the other three bedrooms. Access to the fantastic amenities.
